{"word":"συμπόσιον","slug":"συμπόσιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συμπόσιον, ου, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:συμπίνω\">συμπίνω</a></el>] by metonymy the central <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mng.\">mng.</a> of <el>σ.</el> ‘banquet’ is transferred to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a>: ‘group of diners, party’, hence the distributive <el>συμπόσια συμπόσια</el> is to be rendered ‘in parties’ <b><a href='B:480 6:39'>Mk 6:39</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συμποσία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συμπρεσβύτερος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}